 243++7DCA              ; In :
 244++7DCA              ;   SP+0  - x-coordinate of scroll bar top-left, in pixels
 245++7DCA              ;   SP+2  - y-coordinate of scroll bar top-left, in pixels
 246++7DCA              ;   SP+4  - width of scroll bar, in pixels. if width is greater than height, the scroll bar is drawn horizontally
 247++7DCA              ;   SP+6  - height of scroll bar, in pixels. if height is greater than width, the scroll bar is drawn vertically
 248++7DCA              ;   SP+8  - by default the scroll bar is drawn with a 3D effect and the value of options is zero. options OPT_FLAT remove the 3D effect and its value is 256
 249++7DCA              ;   SP+10 - displayed value of scroll bar, between 0 and range inclusive
 250++7DCA              ;   SP+12 - size
 251++7DCA              ;   SP+14 - maximum value
